Description:
You notice that a nearby granary has the door open and some strange noises come from it.

When you look inside, you discover some farmers wandering aimlessly, in them you can clearly see a strange flower grappling their hearts.

It seems that those infected by the flowers have no way to turn back to normal.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
